      ' Narrated `Abdullah bin Mas`ud:\n\nI said, O Allahs Messenger (ﷺ)! Which is the biggest sin? He said, To set up rivals to Allah by worshipping others though He alone has created you. I asked, What is next? He said, To kill your child lest it should share your food. I asked, What is next? He said, To commit illegal sexual intercourse with the wife of your neighbor.',
