      ' Narrated Jabir bin `Abdullah Al-Ansari:\n\nA man from the tribe of Bani Aslam came to Allahs Messenger (ﷺ) and Informed him that he had committed illegal sexual intercourse and bore witness four times against himself. Allahs Messenger (ﷺ) ordered him to be stoned to death as he was a married Person.',
