    hadithEnglish:
      ' Narrated Ibn `Abbas:\n\nThe Prophet (ﷺ) cursed the effeminate men and those women who assume the similitude (manners) of men. He also said, Turn them out of your houses. He turned such-and-such person out, and `Umar also turned out such-and-such person.',
