      ' Narrated Sahl bin Sa`d:\n\nI witnessed the case of Lian (the case of a man who charged his wife for committing illegal sexual intercourse when I was fifteen years old. The Prophet (ﷺ) ordered that they be divorced, and the husband said, If I kept her, I would be a liar. I remember that Az-Zubair also said, (It was said) that if that woman brought forth the child with such-and-such description, her husband would prove truthful, but if she brought it with such-and-such description looking like a Wahra (a red insect), he would prove untruthful. I heard Az-Zubair also saying, Finally she gave birth to a child of description which her husband disliked .',
