      ' Narrated Abu Zura bin `Amr bin Jarir:\n\nThe Prophet (ﷺ) said during Hajjat-al-Wada`, Let the people be quiet and listen to me. After me, do not become disbelievers, by striking (cutting) the necks of one another.',
