    hadithEnglish:
      ' Narrated Muhammad bin `Ali:\n\n`Ali was told that Ibn `Abbas did not see any harm in the Muta marriage. `Ali said, Allahs Messenger (ﷺ) forbade the Muta marriage on the Day of the battle of Khaibar and he forbade the eating of donkeys meat. Some people said, If one, by a tricky way, marries temporarily, his marriage is illegal. Others said, The marriage is valid but its condition is illegal.',
