    hadithEnglish:
      ' Narrated `Amr bin Ash-Sharid:\n\nAbu Rafi` sold a house to Sa`d bin Malik for four-hundred Mithqal of gold, and said, If I had not heard the Prophet (ﷺ) saying, The neighbor has more right to be taken care of by his neighbor (than anyone else), then I would not have sold it to you.',
