    hadithEnglish:
      ' Narrated `Aisha:\n\nAllahs Messenger (ﷺ) said (to me), You were shown to me twice in (my) dream. Behold, a man was carrying you in a silken piece of cloth and said to me, She is your wife, so uncover her, and behold, it was you. I would then say (to myself), If this is from Allah, then it must happen. ',
