      ' Narrated `Abdullah bin Hisham:\n\nwho was born during the lifetime of the Prophet (ﷺ) that his mother, Zainab bint Humaid had taken him to Allahs Messenger (ﷺ) and said, O Allahs Messenger (ﷺ)! Take his Pledge of allegiance (for Islam). The Prophet (ﷺ) said, He (`Abdullah bin Hisham) is a little child, and passed his hand over his head and invoked Allah for him. `Abdullah bin Hisham used to slaughter one sheep as a sacrifice on behalf of all of his family.',
