    hadithEnglish:
      ' Narrated Jabir bin `Abdullah:\n\nWhen the (following) Verse was revealed to Allahs Messenger (ﷺ): Say: He has power to send torment on you from above,..(6.65) he said, O Allah! I seek refuge with Your Face (from that punishment). And when this was revealed: ..or from beneath your feet. (6.65) he said, O Allah! I seek refuge with Your Face (from that). And when this Verse was revealed: ..or to cover you with confusion in partystrife, and make you to taste the violence of one another,...(6.65) he said: These two warnings are easier (than the previous ones).',
