      ' Narrated Mu`adh bin Jabal:\n\nThe Prophet (ﷺ) said, O Mu`adh! Do you know what Allahs Right upon His slaves is? I said, Allah and His Apostle know best. The Prophet (ﷺ) said, To worship Him (Allah) Alone and to join none in worship with Him (Allah). Do you know what their right upon Him is? I replied, Allah and His Apostle know best. The Prophet (ﷺ) said, Not to punish them (if they do so).',
